high_descs: turn right and walk forwards until you reach the rug beneath you, then turn left and walk forwards to the kitchen counter to the right of the stove
grab the knife off of the kitchen counter in front of you
move to the left a bit and face the kitchen counter again
cut up the apple there on the counter top
back up a bit to make some space, then face the kitchen counter again
place the knife inside of the cabinet below to the bottom right, which is to the right of the stove
move left a bit and then forwards to the kitchen counter to the right of the stove again
grab an apple slice off of the kitchen counter there
turn around and walk over to the microwave on the left side of the room at the end of the room
place the apple slice inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn around and walk to the kitchen table at the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the fridge ahead
place the apple slice inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved apple slice inside of the kitchen fridge

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk a bit, then turn left and head towards the counter with the knife on it.
Pick up the knife.
Face the apple.
Cut the apple.
Turn 360 degrees and face the cupboard under the counter.
Open the cupboard, place the knife in and close it.
Face the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Turn to the right and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, close the door, cook the apple, and then take it out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the other end of the room, then turn right and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the slice of apple in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Cook a slice of apple and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn to your left
Go to the counter that is in the kitchen
Grab the knife from on the counter
Turn to the left
Turn to the right and walk to the end of the counter where the fruit is
Use the knife to slice the fruit
Then pick the sliced fruit up from on the counter
Turn to the right and start walking straight
Got to the microwave and stick the fruit in there
Shut the microwave door and turn the microwave on
After the microwave is done take grab fruit that is in the microwave
Carry the fruit to the fridge and put the fruit up
Turn around, walk halfway across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
take a step to the left to face the apple on the counter.
cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Take a step to the right and face the cabinet below the sink.
Put the knife in the cabinet below the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the apple on the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right to face the cabinet.
Place the piece of apple on the top shelf of the cabinet on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Heat a piece of apple as well as store the apple in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left after passing the oven, go forward to the counter to the right of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Take a step to the left.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Move back from the counter, face the counter.
Put the knife in the bottom cabinet to the right of the oven.
Go forward to the counter where the apple is.
Take a piece of the apple from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the apple on the lower right shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in a fridge.
